social_posts.post_text: the dreaded day 😩😩 maybe it’s just me but i always get nervous every year when these come out, hoping that the number shows more streams than the year before. last year i was STOKED about my numbers and released a ton of tracks, but this year looked a little different and i’ve concluded that that’s okay!! celebrating the wins and the numbers is always a good thing and it keeps us going as artists, BUT remember that the numbers don’t show live performances, upcoming songs, personal growth, friendships made, connections made, and overall happiness. i got less streams than last year and wanted to show that - but feel like this year i grew the most as an artist and a person while also joining the most amazing team @cultiv8artists ❤️ celebrate ALL of the wins, not just the numbers. thank you all so much for listening to my music, your support means the world to me seriously. i couldn’t be happier with 2022 <3 #spotifywrapped #spotifyforartists
👾👾 @lensa.ai
